docs {
  Permanently deletes a flight request record.


**Auth:** Session cookie (`readi_auth_token`). Requires `view_planning_advanced` permission.

  **Used in:**
  - `src/components/operation/FlightRequestsTable.tsx` — delete action on flight requests
}
